        "en": "The purpose of this project is to reconstruct the genealogical tree of the sciences, namely, the \"table of contents\" of the history of human knowledge. As such, the present atlas should be of interest not only to historians, but also to philosophers, sociologists and anyone interested in the history of their discipline and its relations to other sciences."
